The paper discusses the development of a Visual Data Management System (VDMS) that manages, queries, and indexes the predictions of deep learning models. This involves data management, computer vision, and artificial intelligence, which are all covered by the cs.DB, cs.CV, and cs.AI sub-categories. The paper also discusses query optimization and automated physical design, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
